  "title": "Project Manager",
  "description": "<p>An industry leader in Timber and Metal Doors manufacturer & implementation with almost half a century history in Singapore. We are currently recruiting for our business transformation and expansion. We seek individuals who are motived, independent and can support our vision towards establishing our international footprint.</p><p>We are currently looking for<strong> Project Manager </strong>who will facilitate out project requirements with the factory and logistic department. <br /><br />Job Description :</p><ol><li>Manage the site coordination between various parties.</li><li>Manage and review the product specifications, all related schedules, etc to ensure timely delivery and installation of materials to the assigned projects.</li><li>Resource planning in terms of manpower, materials and tools to ensure internal and external resources are sufficient to cope with project orders.</li><li>Attend site meetings, conduct site survey and measurements, issue projects orders, attend to defects and other necessary duties to facilitate the successful handover of the project.</li></ol>",
